{"tid":741701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波指單邊保護主義不可取　美方霸凌無信用","createTime":"2018-07-14T02:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T15:18:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4886e120d779c909332548fac6514a0530ebae3d","tid":741701,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:03:34.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波表示，單邊保護主義是非常不可取，美國總統特朗普上任後，與中國談判過幾次但又推翻結果，令人感覺無信用和霸凌，希望美國回歸理性，利用世貿的多邊協商模式解決爭議。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波在一個電台節目表示，中美貿易糾紛似乎會持續一段時間，可能有政治考慮，企圖打亂內地發展步伐。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於有報道指，中央會成立一個小組負責大灣區事務，國務院副總理韓正出任組長，港澳特首會在小組內。陳茂波表示，如果有這個機制是相當好，令香港能直接參與相關討論和提供意見。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406938-20180714.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406938-20180714.htm&d=QWEDxSi9giyc4bMK95eNSwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=befdcee0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406938-20180714.htm&h=688558cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406938-20180714.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8ff28c757dff0cc4c44de9e5ccc95087910109f8","tid":741701,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7002d59f75e75965a18d708fe209747c7342e4cd","tid":741701,"uid":76310,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"奶共到<br />\n同中共強國官員一樣<br />\n<br />\n一國一制<br />\n取消香港關係法啦"},{"pid":"2c406c6a8e3a838622e7dc8fc387fd9d207fcf15","tid":741701,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6902b32a5acd90a5188e6f569cc7d8b7fdcc652c","tid":741701,"uid":22422,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"中國違反咗自由貿易十幾廿年<br />\n又侵犯知識產權<br />\